    搜索二叉树的实现

    前言:搜索二叉树的左子树的值比该节点的值要小,右子树的值比该节点的值要大

    # 01、代码实现

    # -*- ecoding: utf-8 -*-
# @ModuleName: btree
# @Mail: 15717163552@163.com
# @Author: mozhouqiu
# @Time: 2022/5/19 11:06
from collections import deque


class BitreeNode:
    def __init__(self,val):
        self.data = val
        self.lchild = None
        self.rchild = None

class Bitree:
    def __init__(self):
        self.root = None

    #前序遍历(递归实现)
    def pre_order(self,root):
        if root:
            print(root.data,end=',')
            self.pre_order(root.lchild)
            self.pre_order(root.rchild)

    #中序遍历(递归实现)
    def in_order(self,root):
        if root:
            self.in_order(root.lchild)
            print(root.data, end=',')
            self.in_order(root.rchild)

    #后序遍历(递归实现)
    def post_order(self,root):
        if root:
            self.post_order(root.lchild)
            self.post_order(root.rchild)
            print(root.data, end=',')

    #层次遍历(广度优先):
    def level_order(self,root):
        queue = deque()
        queue.append(root)
        while len(queue)>0:
            node = queue.popleft()
            print(node.data, end=',')
            if node.lchild:
                queue.append(node.lchild)
            if node.rchild:
                queue.append(node.rchild)



    #插入非递归实现
    def insert_no_rec(self,val):
        if not self.root:
            self.root = BitreeNode(val)
        else:
            p = self.root
            while True:
                if val < p.data:
                    if not p.lchild:
                        p.lchild = BitreeNode(val)
                        return
                    else:
                        p = p.lchild
                elif val > p.data:
                    if not p.rchild:
                        p.rchild = BitreeNode(val)
                        return
                    else:
                        p = p.rchild
                else:
                    raise ValueError("repetitive value")

b = Bitree()
b.insert_no_rec(10)
b.insert_no_rec(9)
b.insert_no_rec(11)
b.insert_no_rec(8)
b.insert_no_rec(12)

b.pre_order(b.root)
b.in_order(b.root)
b.post_order(b.root)
b.level_order(b.root)
